snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise - Announce Trailer | Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, Game Pass, PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
The gates to Kamura are opening up for even more Hunters! Monster Hunter Rise comes to Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, Game Pass, PS5, and PS4 on Jan 20!

The massive expansion, Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak, launches in Spring 2023.

Pre-order Monster Hunter Rise now! 
Microsoft Store: https://bit.ly/MHRise_Xbox
PlayStation Store: https://bit.ly/MHRise_PS

Learn more about Monster Hunter Rise: 
https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise-xwp/
